property.name: script
property.value:
## R-chart script.
## For use with GoldenCheetah.
## tested on GC.version() is "DEV-V3.5 1705"
##
xtext<-"Pace/100m (min:sec)"
ytext<-"Stroke Rate/min (srm)"

pushoff<-3 ## push-off compensation (m)
strokestyle<-1## 1=freestyle, 2=backstroke, 3=breaststroke, 4=butterfly
## plot colors
regionlowfill<-adjustcolor("#5076a3",alpha.f=.6)
regionlowborder<-"#5076a3"
regionhighfill<-adjustcolor("#a34b49",alpha.f=.6)
regionhighborder<-"#a34b49"
sb_size_min<-1
sb_size_max<-15
sb_alpha<-0.5
## plot symbols
pl25<-21
pl50<-22
plx<-23
#plot limits
xmin<-130
xmax<-60
ymin<-30
ymax<-100

darken <- function(color, factor=1.4){
 col <- col2rgb(color)
 col <- col/factor
 col <- rgb(t(col), maxColorValue=255)
}

stroketext<-list("Freestyle", "Backstroke", "Breaststroke", "Butterfly")
header<-paste(stroketext[strokestyle]," stroke rate chart")

## plot
par(mar=c(6,6,3,0))
plot(NULL,NULL, xlim=c(xmin,xmax),ylim=c(ymin,ymax), type="n",xlab="",ylab="", xaxt="n", yaxt="n")
## ticks
at=seq(xmin,xmax,-10)
axis(1, at=at, tcl=-0.8, labels=sprintf("%d:%02d",at%/%60,at%%60))##major x-axis
axis(1, at=seq(xmin,xmax,-1), labels=NA)##minor x-axis
axis(2, at=seq(ymin,ymax,10), tcl=-0.8, las=2)##major y-axis
axis(2, at=seq(ymin,ymax,1), labels=NA)##minor y-axis

## region low
##lines(x_region1,region_low,type="l", col="blue")
x_region1<- c(130 ,120 ,110 ,100 ,90 ,80 ,70 ,60)
region_low<-c(50.0,50.8,51.6,53.0,54.5,57.0,61.0,67.0)
polygon(c(xmin,x_region1,xmax),c(ymin,region_low,ymin),col=regionlowfill,border=regionlowborder)
##text(127,31,"Low Stroke rate", col="#0000FF", cex=1)
mtext("Low Stroke rate",1, line=-3.5, col="#0000FF", cex=1)

## region high
##lines(x_region2,region_high,type="l", col="red")
x_region2<- c(130 ,120 ,110 ,100 ,95.5,90 ,80 ,70 ,67)
region_high<-c(61.8,63.4,65.2,68.0,70.0,73.1,83.1,96.0,100.0)
polygon(c(xmin,x_region2),c(ymax,region_high),col=regionhighfill,border=regionhighborder)
##text(126.9,99,"High Stroke rate", col="#ff0000", cex=1)
mtext("High Stroke rate",3, line=-3.5, col="#ff0000", cex=1)

## region OK
##polygon(c(x_region1,rev(c(x_region2,xmax))),c(region_low,rev(c(region_high,ymax))),col="gray",border="gray")

## title
title(main=header,cex.main=2.0,xlab=xtext,ylab=ytext)

## grid lines
grid(col="#606060", lty="solid", lwd=0.5)

## plot values, use available swim data(XDATA)
metrics<-GC.activity.metrics(compare=TRUE)
activities<-GC.activity(compare=TRUE)
for(a in 1:length(activities)){
 if ("SWIM_TYPE" %in% names(activities[[a]]$activity))##swim activity?
 {
 swim<-activities[[a]]$activity[which(as.numeric(activities[[a]]$activity$SWIM_TYPE)==strokestyle),]
 if ("Pool_Length" %in% names(metrics[[a]]$metrics)){Pool_Length<-as.numeric(metrics[[a]]$metrics$Pool_Length)}else{Pool_Length<-0}
 pointfill<-activities[[a]]$color
 pointfill<-adjustcolor(activities[[a]]$color,alpha.f=sb_alpha)
 pointborder<-darken(activities[[a]]$color)

 if (Pool_Length==25){sb1<-pl25}
 else {if (Pool_Length==50){sb1<-pl50}
 else {sb1<-plx}}

 pace<-swim$SWIM_DURATION*100/Pool_Length
 sr<-(60*2*swim$SWIM_STROKES/swim$SWIM_DURATION)/(1-pushoff/Pool_Length)## 2arms per minute, incl pushoff compensation
 ##lines(pace, sr, type="p", col=pointborder, bg=pointfill, pch=sb1, cex=pointsize)
 pl<-lowess(round(pace),sr)
 xn<-table(pl$x)
 f<-xn/max(xn)
 lines(pl$x[!duplicated(pl$x)],pl$y[!duplicated(pl$x)], type="o", col=pointborder, bg=pointfill, pch=sb1, cex=sb_size_min+(sb_size_max-sb_size_min)*f)
 }
}
legend("top", legend=c("25m","50m","custom"), pch=c(pl25,pl50,plx), horiz=TRUE, bty="n", xpd=TRUE, inset=c(0), pt.cex=2)
